	<p>Additional $5.00/mo. credit for 12 months after signing up for Auto Bill Pay and with activation of the BUSINESS INFORMATION package or above. Additional $5 per month Bundle credit for 12 months when ordered with or added to an existing CenturyLink Core Connect package.</p>
