	<p id="offers"><b>PROMOTIONAL OFFERS:</b> The information below applies to promotional offers for services. These limited-time promotional offers may include special monthly pricing on services, associated items available with your purchase of services, and unique savings and performance capabilities. All promotional offers, unless otherwise indicated, end January 31, 2012. Promotional offers may be limited to specific locations, which may change without notice. </p>
	<p><b>3-months free &mdash; Business Support Pack:</b> Requires 12-month term and new or upgrade to existing High-Speed Internet with minimum 1.5mbps HSI speed tier. Applies to Standard Pack and Premium Pack only. Appears as credit on three invoices beginning with the first full month invoice. To avoid services charges, customer must contact CenturyLink before the end of the free billing periods and cancel services. Excludes, taxes, fees and surcharges. Service-specific terms set forth in the Business Support Pack service paragraph above also apply</p>
	<p><b>6-months free HSI Upgrade:</b> Minimum 12-month term required. Available for all speed tiers. Credit each month for six months equal to the difference in the monthly service charge between customer's current and upgraded speed tiers will appear on customers first or second invoice after upgrade. Excludes taxes, fees and surcharges. Service-specific terms set forth in the High-Speed Internet service paragraph above also apply.</p>
	<p><b>$5 Bill Credit with Verizon Wireless:</b> Applies when new or existing 1.5 mbps or higher HSI small business customers with  minimum two-year term activate through CenturyLink a new Verizon Wireless line of service with minimum two-year term. One $5 credit per account issued each month for up to 24 consecutive months on HSI portion of customer's CenturyLink bill. Verizon Wireless services billed separately by Verizon. Service-specific terms set forth in the High-Speed Internet service paragraph above also apply.</p>
